    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Dev Role\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to thank you for your interest in the Senior Dev role at our Austin-based company. Your enthusiasm and technical prowess were truly impressive, and we had the pleasure of getting to know you during the final interview.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with a candidate whose experience aligns more closely with our specific cloud architecture needs. This decision was not easy, as we were genuinely impressed by your skills and potential. We understand how tough it can be to let go of a candidate who we believe in so much, and we want you to know that it was a difficult decision for our panel.\n\nWe sincerely appreciate the time and effort you invested in your application and interview process. Your talent and dedication are commendable, and we wish you the best of luck in your future endeavors. We hope to stay in touch and perhaps cross paths again in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
      "source": "target",
